Message Id:		1129886
Message Type:	Change Request
Version:		75.00.16
Priority:		2
Responsible:	Marco Paskamp


Feature description:
For performance enhancement the driver caches the rowset size and avoids internal calls to the underlaying interface SQLDBC.

